    <section name="Mandatory or optional field">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to define a field as mandatory or as optional.</span>

   <div class='screenshot'>
     <img src="../../../../images/inars/mandatory_or_optional.png" alt='Mandatory or optional screenshot'/> 
     <p>
      In a document type, a mandatory field (which is a date field).
     </p>
   </div>

   <p>
    While adding a field to a document type, e.g. 
    a <a href='./add_date_to_documenttype.html'>date field</a>,
    one should decide if the field 
    should be <a href='../concepts/mandatory_or_optional.html'>mandatory or optional</a>.
    Check the mandatory checkbox the make the field mandatory  (far right, almost at the bottom).
    If the box is unchecked, the field is optional. 
   </p>

